movies.title: Shrek
movies.synopsis: On a mission to retrieve a beautiful princess from the clutches of a fierce dragon, a grumpy ogre teams up with a witty donkey.

movies.title: Shrek 2
movies.director: Andrew Adamson, Kelly Asbury, Conrad Vernon
movies.synopsis: Back in Far Far Away, Shrek and Fiona announce their union, but Prince Charming's sinister plan threatens their everlasting marital bliss.

movies.title: Shrek the Third
movies.synopsis: The kingdom needs an heir, and Shrek, Donkey and Cat set out to find one, just when Shrek learns he's going to become a daddy.

movies.title: Howl's Moving Castle
movies.synopsis: Sophie is a teenager who works in a hat store in a town like many, but her life takes a complete turn when a witch transforms her into an old woman.

movies.title: Spirited Away
movies.synopsis: Chihiro enters a magical world ruled by a witch, where those who do not obey are transformed into animals.

movies.title: Blade Runner 2049
movies.synopsis: The contents of a tomb attract the interest of a powerful tycoon. In charge of the mission is officer K, who goes in search of a lost legend.

movies.title: Spaceman
movies.synopsis: Six months after embarking on a lonely mission, an astronaut faces the problems of his marriage with the help of the mysterious creature he found on his spacecraft.

movies.title: Shutter Island
movies.synopsis: While investigating the disappearance of an inmate in a psychiatric hospital, a federal marshal becomes entangled in a web of lies and begins to doubt himself.

movies.title: Tau
movies.synopsis: He kidnapped her to use her as a guinea pig to debug the artificial intelligence he created. She, despite her age, learned from the street and knows how to sneak away.

movies.title: The Social Network
movies.synopsis: Harvard student Mark Zuckerberg goes after an idea that propels him to internet success, but also causes him legal trouble and broken ties.

movies.title: Society of the Snow
movies.synopsis: The flight of a rugby team crashes on a glacier in the Andes. The few passengers who survive the crash find themselves in one of the world's toughest environments to survive.

movies.title: White Chicks
movies.synopsis: Two disgraced FBI agents go way undercover in an effort to protect hotel heiresses the Wilson sisters from a kidnapping plot.

movies.title: Pride & Prejudice
movies.synopsis: Sparks fly when spirited Elizabeth Bennet meets single, rich, and proud Mr. Darcy. But Mr. Darcy reluctantly finds himself falling in love with a woman beneath his class. Can each overcome their own pride and prejudice?

movies.title: Pretty Woman
movies.synopsis: A man in a legal but hurtful business needs an escort for some social events, and hires a beautiful prostitute he meets... only to fall in love.

movies.title: The Lady of Silence: The Mataviejitas Murders
movies.synopsis: Between 1998 and 2005, a wave of murders targeting elderly women hit Mexico City, triggering the hunt for and capture of a most unlikely suspect.

movies.title: The Three Deaths of Marisela Escobedo
movies.synopsis: Follows a mother's tireless crusade to jail her daughter's murderer after Mexico's justice system failed to do so.

movies.title: Inside the Mind of a Cat
movies.synopsis: Cat experts dive into the mind of the feline to reveal the true capabilities of the pouncing pet in this captivating and cuddly documentary.

movies.title: The Tinder Swindler
movies.synopsis: Posing as a wealthy, jet-setting diamond mogul, he wooed women online, then conned them out of millions of dollars. Now some victims plan for payback.

movies.title: Stutz
movies.synopsis: Follow Hill and his therapist as he has candid discussions of mental health and the progressively worsening anxiety attacks related to movie promotion that have turned his dream job into a nightmare.

movies.title: Cyber Hell: Exposing an Internet Horror
movies.synopsis: Anonymous and exploitative, a network of online chat rooms ran rampant with sex crimes. The hunt to take down its operators required guts and tenacity.

movies.title: Einstein and the Bomb
movies.synopsis: What happened after Einstein fled Nazi Germany? Using archival footage and his own words, this docudrama dives into the mind of a tortured genius.

movies.title: To Kill a Tiger
movies.synopsis: Ranjit, a farmer in India, takes on the fight of his life when he demands justice for his 13-year-old daughter, the victim of a brutal gang rape. His decision to support his daughter is virtually unheard of, and his journey unprecedented.

movies.title: Damsel
movies.synopsis: A dutiful damsel agrees to marry a handsome prince, only to find the royal family has recruited her as a sacrifice to repay an ancient debt.

movies.title: Top Gun: Maverick
movies.synopsis: After thirty years, Maverick is still pushing the envelope as a top naval aviator, but must confront ghosts of his past when he leads TOP GUN's elite graduates on a mission that demands the ultimate sacrifice from those chosen to fly it.

movies.title: The Boy in the Striped Pajamas
movies.synopsis: Through the innocent eyes of Bruno, the eight-year-old son of the commandant at a German concentration camp, a forbidden friendship with a Jewish boy on the other side of the camp fence has startling and unexpected consequences.

movies.title: Good Will Hunting
movies.synopsis: Will Hunting, a janitor at M.I.T., has a gift for mathematics, but needs help from a psychologist to find direction in his life.

movies.title: Despicable Me
movies.synopsis: Gru, a criminal mastermind, adopts three orphans as pawns to carry out the biggest heist in history. His life takes an unexpected turn when the little girls see the evildoer as their potential father.

movies.title: Despicable Me 2
movies.synopsis: When Gru, the world's most super-bad turned super-dad has been recruited by a team of officials to stop lethal muscle and a host of Gru's own, He has to fight back with new gadgetry, cars, and more minion madness.

movies.title: Despicable Me 3
movies.director: Kyle Balda, Pierre Coffin, Eric Guillon
movies.synopsis: Gru meets his long-lost, charming, cheerful, and more successful twin brother Dru, who wants to team up with him for one last criminal heist.

movies.title: The Impossible
movies.synopsis: The story of a tourist family in Thailand caught in the destruction and chaotic aftermath of the 2004 Indian Ocean tsunami.

movies.title: Marley & Me
movies.synopsis: A family learns important life lessons from their adorable, but naughty and neurotic dog.

movies.title: 13 Going on 30
movies.synopsis: Unpopular schoolgirl Jenna Rink makes an unusual wish on her birthday. Miraculously, her wish comes true and the 13-year-old Jenna wakes up the next day as a 30-year-old woman.

movies.title: Just Go with It
movies.synopsis: On a weekend trip to Hawaii, a plastic surgeon convinces his loyal assistant to pose as his soon-to-be-divorced wife in order to cover up a careless lie he told to his much-younger girlfriend.

movies.title: Ella Enchanted
movies.synopsis: Ella is under a spell to be constantly obedient, a fact she must hide from her new stepfamily in order to protect the prince of the land, her friend for whom she's falling.

movies.title: Twilight
movies.synopsis: When Bella Swan moves to a small town in the Pacific Northwest, she falls in love with Edward Cullen, a mysterious classmate who reveals himself to be a 108-year-old vampire.

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: New Moon
movies.synopsis: Edward leaves Bella after an attack that nearly claimed her life, and, in her depression, she falls into yet another difficult relationship - this time with her close friend, Jacob Black.

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
movies.synopsis: As a string of mysterious killings grips Seattle, Bella, whose high school graduation is fast approaching, is forced to choose between her love for vampire Edward and her friendship with werewolf Jacob.

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1
movies.synopsis: The Quileutes close in on expecting parents Edward and Bella, whose unborn child poses a threat to the Wolf Pack and the towns people of Forks.

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 2
movies.synopsis: After the birth of Renesmee/Nessie, the Cullens gather other vampire clans in order to protect the child from a false allegation that puts the family in front of the Volturi.

movies.title: The Hunger Games
movies.synopsis: Katniss Everdeen voluntarily takes her younger sister's place in the Hunger Games: a televised competition in which two teenagers from each of the twelve Districts of Panem are chosen at random to fight to the death.

movies.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
movies.synopsis: Katniss Everdeen and Peeta Mellark become targets of the Capitol after their victory in the 74th Hunger Games sparks a rebellion in the Districts of Panem.

movies.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 1
movies.synopsis: Katniss Everdeen is in District 13 after she shatters the games forever. Under the leadership of President Coin and the advice of her trusted friends, Katniss spreads her wings as she fights to save Peeta and a nation moved by her courage.

movies.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 2
movies.synopsis: Katniss and a team of rebels from District 13 prepare for the final battle that will decide the fate of Panem.

movies.title: Lover Stalker Killer
movies.synopsis: In this twisting documentary, a mechanic tries online dating for the first time and meets a woman who takes romantic obsession to a deadly extreme.

movies.title: Guillermo del Toro's Pinocchio
movies.synopsis: A father's wish magically brings a wooden boy to life in Italy, giving him a chance to care for the child.

movies.title: Tell Me Who I Am
movies.synopsis: After losing his memory in an accident, Alex Lewis trusts his twin brother, Marcus, to tell him about his past only to discover that he's hiding a dark secret about their childhood.

movies.title: Anna Nicole Smith: You Don't Know Me
movies.synopsis: Anna Nicole Smith, featuring never before seen footage of the iconic Playboy and Guess jeans model, who blazed a trail through the 90s before her tragic death at the age of 39.

movies.title: Capturing the Killer Nurse
movies.synopsis: This documentary reveals how investigators proved ICU nurse Charles Cullen was killing patients — and how close he came to getting away with murder.

movies.title: The Mystery of Marilyn Monroe: The Unheard Tapes
movies.synopsis: Explores the mystery surrounding the death of movie icon Marilyn Monroe through previously unheard interviews with her inner circle.

movies.title: Wham!
movies.synopsis: Through archival interviews and footage, George Michael and Andrew Ridgeley relive the arc of their Wham career, from '70s best buds to '80s pop icons.
